<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently Navigation supports rel and rev attributes, but these are only used by the Links view helper.
I've read multiple people needing rel="nofollow" on anchors, and although it's easily implemented using 
a custom view helper, it's also no work to implement this in the framework itself. So why not support it?</p>

<p>Also see: <a href="http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-7733">http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-7733</a></p>

